  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2021, the average price of a wedding dress typically ranged from about $1,000 to $3,000. However, prices can vary significantly based on factors such as brand, designer, the materials used, and the complexity of the design. Custom-made gowns and designer dresses can cost much more, sometimes exceeding $10,000. \n\nFor the most accurate and current information, I recommend checking recent sources or bridal shops, as prices can fluctuate and trends may change over time.",
